data.description: Welcome to this upgraded and well maintained 3BD/2.5BA home with an open concept floor plan on the main level. No neighbors on two sides and located at the end of a shared driveway. A light and bright main living area features a comfortable living room with fireplace, a formal dining area, and kitchen with stainless steel appliances and white cabinetry. A slider off the dining room leads to a private fenced yard with ample space for outdoor dining and entertaining. A laundry closet is situated off the kitchen and 1/2 bath. Upstairs you will find all three bedrooms including the primary bedroom with en-suite bath. Updates include leased solar on a newer energy-saving Owens Corning roof, espresso hardwood flooring, smart home features and partial dual pane windows. There is a 2 car attached garage with additional space for several other cars or an airstream/boat. The property lies adjacent to the Joe Rodata pedestrian and cyclist trail. Low-maintenance landscaping. Mins to Sebastopol or downtown Santa Rosa via Highway 12. Close to shopping, schools and an array of amenities.
